OL,3,CWoman left to die in 'barely
OL,4,Cinhabitable' home was 'unlawfully
OL,5,Ckilled'
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Tim
OL,8,FScott has this report.
OL,10,FA woman with Down's Syndrome who died
OL,11,Fin an emancipated state at her home
OL,12,Fwas unlawfully killed, an inquest has
OL,13,Fconcluded.
OL,15,FDebbie Leitch, 24, was discovered dead
OL,16,Fat her family home in Blackpool in
OL,17,FAugust 2019.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
