OL,3,CWoman left to die in 'barely
OL,4,Cinhabitable' home was 'unlawfully
OL,5,Ckilled'
OL,7,FShe weighed under four stone and had
OL,8,Fbeen abandoned by her mother to die
OL,9,Falone, in pain and in squalid
OL,10,Fconditions, described as "barely
OL,11,Finhabitable."
OL,13,FDebbie's mother Elaine Clarke, 49, was
OL,14,Fjailed in 2021 for nine years and
OL,15,Fseven months after pleading guilty to
OL,16,Fgross negligence manslaughter after
OL,17,Finitially denying the offence.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
