OL,4,Cinhabitable' home was 'unlawfully
OL,5,Ckilled'
OL,7,FA social worker and carer did not ask
OL,8,Fenough questions about her condition
OL,9,Fand they were easily influenced by her
OL,10,Fmother, Elaine, who had hidden the
OL,11,Ftruth about her neglect.
OL,13,FConcluding the case on Wednesday, 16
OL,14,FOctober, Mr Wilson did not issue a
OL,15,FPrevention of Future Deaths report as
OL,16,Fhe was satisfied the professional
OL,17,Fagencies who had failed Debbie have
OL,18,Fsince changed their habits.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
