OL,7,FHe said the cause of her death was
OL,8,Fsevere emaciation, neglect and scabies
OL,9,Fand ruled she was unlawfully killed.
OL,11,FKaren Smith, Director of Adult
OL,12,FServices, said: "Since the time of
OL,13,FDeborah's untimely death our thoughts
OL,14,Fand condolences have been with her
OL,15,Fextended family.
