OL,7,F"Deborah's tragic death has taught us
OL,8,Fa lot. Following the review, changes
OL,9,Fhave been implemented and are now
OL,10,Fembedded in our social work practice.
OL,12,F"Our processes have been improved,
OL,13,Falong with the way we share
OL,14,Finformation internally, with other
OL,15,Fcouncils, our partners and local
OL,16,Fagencies in order to improve the care
OL,17,Fwe provide to vulnerable residents.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
