OL,7,F"We have also shared the learning more
OL,8,Fwidely through the Safeguarding Board,
OL,9,Fwhich has also overseen the assurance
OL,10,Fthat the actions identified have been
OL,11,Ftaken."
OL,13,FThe inquest earlier heard from former
OL,14,FCherish UK carer Scott Worthington who
OL,15,Fdescribed the environment Debbie lived
OL,16,Fin as "very dirty" and how there was
OL,17,F"chaos" in the house.
