OL,7,FMr Worthington also described hearing
OL,8,Floud crying from a room upstairs and,
OL,9,Fon the one occasion he saw Debbie in
OL,10,Fperson, he was shocked by her
OL,11,Fappearance saying she was gaunt and
OL,12,F'looked like a skeleton'.
OL,14,FA written statement from another
OL,15,Fformer carer, Solomon Thornton, who
OL,16,Fvisited the house to deal with another
OL,17,Fmatter described finding "bottles of
OL,18,Furine".
